thread.title: One passenger dead after Southwest engine failure

title: One passenger dead after Southwest engine failure
text:
One passenger dead after Southwest engine failure 4:00am IST - 01:18 
An engine on a Dallas-bound Southwest Airlines flight apparently exploded on Tuesday, forcing an emergency landing in Philadelphia as one passenger was killed, according to officials. Yahaira Jacquez reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
